{"tid":1294881,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：風雲色變，陳雲出山。","createTime":"2019-07-08T01:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T20:03:14.000Z","uid":30561,"like":7,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccd5b1e440b88cc24bf0712781083a787c2e6a3","tid":1294881,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:00:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">陳雲：風雲色變，陳雲出山。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja8NhH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja8NhH1.jpg&h=a03726da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91081ccfdfa61348dc587f3b21a9dca6947448ea","tid":1294881,"uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:00:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">香港就快唔屬於香港人，集資買島建立屬於香港人既地方 </span><br />\n<br />\n彈丸之地香港其實有大量嘅有錢人同埋技術人員，二百幾萬人一起做一啲嘢，投資建設新嘅社區， 如果嗰啲小島，係屬於美國/加拿大/英國/澳洲更加會受到軍方嘅保護， 一些西方國家有大規模接收政治難民嘅經驗 ，例如澳洲。西方有著相對優厚的移民吸引力而且比較守承諾，加上香港地有唔少人支持眾籌同埋捐款為香港人做事，買咗嘅地方可以吸引大量嘅投資。 現在香港沒有建立信用評分制度，唔會有人因為信用評分制度影響，所以香港可以自由進出，將多餘嘅錢集資買島。香港不單止要面對2047嘅政治問題還有2050年嘅水位上升嘅氣候問題，重頭開始，係為香港人保留元氣，要養晦轁光，走出悲情的歷史， 唯有堅定建立一個理想的華人世界， 先可以保留正統文化，讓我地後代子孫得以挺直腰幹、開疆闢土、創造榮耀。 <br />\n<br />\n所以如果香港人開始眾籌/捐錢投資屬於香港人既地方， 大家可以參與建設， 最終都係回報畀香港人 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTG Group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ%20&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=d3d375a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ </a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fLfoshW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLfoshW.png&h=7e7ab7be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高登六年前已經開始有討論買島嶼/人工島，但係因為有大量嘅五毛騷擾，難以推廣概念"},{"pid":"f38d694d309caef7ab5a4fa4491ee30ad44588b8","tid":1294881,"uid":107060,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"陳雲佢氣魄更壯<br />\n陳雲出山心中不必驚慌"},{"pid":"11b47252586f50d2487cae7ac531023eda829a8e","tid":1294881,"uid":126283,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:01:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢老過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f7a89923c4160bff8b3093d3486f5ac9290938","tid":1294881,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775c1071ba2c85777343f959a1eeec61083f7ea9","tid":1294881,"uid":55198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:01:39.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"a0d049e4cfa815556c85f4ee0192fe594b31cefc","tid":1294881,"uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f38d694d309caef7ab5a4fa4491ee30ad44588b8","tid":1294881,"uid":107060,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"陳雲佢氣魄更壯<br />\n陳雲出山心中不必驚慌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"陳雲下令左膠即刻驚慌"},{"pid":"b84c2de5fefd814da62b0c85006415e8335a4b6b","tid":1294881,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18249c71ed3aed97339abfb1033c1ac43d9b2446","tid":1294881,"uid":90704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:33:58.000Z","msg":"陳雲不死 卧龍不出"},{"pid":"e80f3c24d599f01aec3dca57b484d76183dde97e","tid":1294881,"uid":61882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/09/07/ClEapZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2FClEapZ.jpg&h=3af98869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳雲式寂滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79511488f